body.description: Vitron-C is a high potency iron supplement formulated with Vitamin C to help your body better absorb iron. The use of an iron pill daily may boost energy by helping to fight fatigue in users with low iron levels* or iron-deficiency anemia. Vitron-C iron supplements contain carbonyl iron which provides gradual and gentle iron absorption and helps minimize constipation*. The added Vitamin C improves iron absorption*. Vitron-C iron with Vitamin C supplement is dye free, gluten free and vegan. Without enough iron, your body can't make enough hemoglobin, a substance that helps red blood cells carry oxygen from the lungs to the body's tissues. Hemoglobin also helps our muscles store and use oxygen. Iron deficiency can affect many body functions. It can delay growth in children, stand in the way of our ability to do work as adults, cause problems during pregnancy and it can even cause heart problems, such as a rapid or irregular heartbeat. If your doctor advises that you have iron deficiency, talk to them about Vitron-C iron supplements. *These statements have not been evaluated by the Food and Drug Administration. This product is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Vitron-C High Potency Iron Supplement Helps Absorb Iron with Vitamin C* Boost energy†* and help support a healthy immune system* with Vitron-C High Potency Iron Supplement with Vitamin C. Formulated to help your body absorb dietary iron more effectively, this daily iron dietary supplement delivers 65mg of elemental iron and 125mg of vitamin C. †Helps fight fatigue in users with low iron levels. *These statements have not been evaluated by the Food and Drug Administration. Easy on the Stomach This mineral supplement has been specially formulated to be easy on the stomach. Vitron-C contains carbonyl iron for gradual and gentle iron absorption, which may minimize the common side effect of constipation. Small Coated Tablets Vitron-C High Potency Iron Supplement makes it easier than ever to get the elemental iron your body needs thanks to its small size and smooth coating. Simply take the nutritional supplement once a day. Helps Combat Iron Deficiency Iron deficiency is a common type of nutritional deficiency. Classic signs of iron deficiency can include feeling tired, feeling weak, and having pale skin color. Taking Vitron-C High Potency Iron Supplement with Vitamin C can help boost energy by helping to fight fatigue in users with low iron level.

Why do we need iron in our diet? Iron plays a key role in helping red blood cells deliver oxygen to the body. Iron deficiency can cause anemia, delay a child’s growth, damage a person's ability to think, and weaken their resistance to infection. What are the signs and symptoms of iron deficiency? Iron deficiency symptoms may include: being very tired, feeling weak, pale skin, shortness of breath, headache, dizziness or lightheadedness, and unusual cravings for non-nutritive substances, such as ice, dirt, or pure starch. Why is vitamin C often recommended along with an iron supplement? Vitamin C helps the body absorb iron. So, whether you are eating iron-rich foods or taking an iron supplement, vitamin C taken at the same time can help with iron absorption. Why did the color of the tablet change from red to grey? The color change is the result of removing dyes from the product. The natural color of iron mixed with vitamin C and inactive ingredients results in a grey tablet. The levels of iron and vitamin C remain the same.
